{"data":[{"date":"18:01 04/08","title":"Gattuso: \"Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Gennaro Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, sau khi m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eeb Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMilan \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rossoneri d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i v\u1edbi Juventus, khi chia tay trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1p Gonzalo Higuain, c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i sao gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng Caldara.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, HLV Gattuso c\u1ee7a Milan t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng: &ldquo;V\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Mattia Caldara l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB, c\u00f2n Gonzalo Higuain t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Milan. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Higuain r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Rossoneri.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\" title=\"Milan chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Milan. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, hay n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Milan, ch\u1eb3ng ai n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Higuain, Caldara v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Milan bay cao tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi h\u1ebft l\u1eddi t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, Gattuso \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Vidal &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ai l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch Vidal. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 anh \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Vidal khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal. V\u00ec sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u01b0? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a cLB, v\u00e0 lu\u1eadt C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p &ldquo;c\u1eebu \u0111en&rdquo;, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5, khi trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan-176-192568.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan-176-192568.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn San...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span><br>\r\nLeonardo Bonucci tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Milan.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5090","checkdouble":"193717"},{"date":"18:40 04/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra sau khi U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 sang H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1.</h2><h2>U23 Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng mang 'h\u00e0ng x\u1ecbn' sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/2177242_105897.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Uzbekistan (tr\u1eafng) kh\u00f4ng mang nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uzbekistan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ec3 ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i\u00a0Odiljon Hamrobekov, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Jasurbek Yakhshiboev hay c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao k\u1ec1u Andrey Sidorov.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV\u00a0Ravshan Khaydarov, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Park Hang-seo \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 danh\u00a0Nuraliev Dilshod.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda L\u0110B\u0110 Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Uzbekistan \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0Olympic Tokyo 2020. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n U23 Uzbekistan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 th\u1ee7\u00a0th\u00e0nh Khamraev Dilshod, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rustamov Oybek, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isroilov Abdujamol, Nurulloev Sukhrob.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 7/8 t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5089","checkdouble":"193718"},{"date":"18:40 04/08","title":"\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn\u00a0</span>Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 Palestine</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i 3/8 v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng 2-1 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/3/28/u23-viet-nam-co-the-nhat-bang-i.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung, h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sang\u00a0hi\u1ec7p 2, khi HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m th\u00eam v\u1ec1 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu Palestine d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u00e8n gi\u0169a c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha b\u00f3ng hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u00fang ta ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u th\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u cao khi b\u1eadt l\u00ean tranh ch\u1ea5p, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y mai 5/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi U23 Oman, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Palestine s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h./.\u00a0<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nHighlight Viet Nam vs Palestine</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong-168-193718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong-168-193718.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra sau khi U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 sang H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1ed3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span><br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\"></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5088","checkdouble":"193719"},{"date":"21:57 04/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: PSG 4-0 Monaco (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/video-tong-hop-psg-40-monaco-sieu-cup-phap-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Monaco thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, PSG d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Monaco thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, PSG d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng:<br>\r\nPSG: Di Mar\u00eda\u00a0 (33', 90+2'), Nkunku\u00a0 (40'), Weah\u00a0 (68')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, PSG v\u1eabn ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n Monaco, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Thiago Silva, Marco Verratti, Adrien Rabiot hay Angel Di Maria. S\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. PSG c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 70%, tung ra 7 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn 2-0.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng PSG vs Monaco 4-0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng PSG vs Monaco 4-0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/di-maria-00.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDi Maria l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 33 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 40, Nkunku nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i N'Soki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Monaco, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. \u0110\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Rony Lopes trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng ch\u1eebng 5m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, Tielemans b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c khi c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thiago Silva \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, PSG ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 PSG c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, N'Soki ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u00f2n Di Maria c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 67 (Timothy Weah) v\u00e0 90 +2 (Di Maria). V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, PSG l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u:<br>\r\nPSG: Buffon; Dagba, Thiago Silva (Bernede 73'), Rimane, N'Soki; Verratti (Neymar 76'), Lass Diarra (Marquinhos 64'), Rabiot; Di Maria, Timothy Weah, Nkunku.<br>\r\nMonaco: Benaglio; Raggu, Glik, Jemerson, Julien Serrano; Aholou, Pele (Diop), Rony Lopes (Mboula 74'), Tielemans, Grandsir (Balde 46'); Jovetic.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5087","checkdouble":"193734"},{"date":"19:58 04/08","title":"Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \"L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf\" l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: LIVERPOOL 5-0 NAPOLI\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Liverpool-vs-Napoli.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>Ngay sau khi thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Klopp - Dortmund 1-3, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp  t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Manchester. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean  \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan s\u1ee9c  m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9  s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a The Kop tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p>Napoli c\u1ee7a HLV Carlo Ancelotti x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed ti\u1ebfp theo cho  Liverpool m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua,  Liverpool lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c  tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Juventus, AC Milan, Inter v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb  chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool. \u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Europa League 2010/11,  Napoli c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m/2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Ancelotti (thay cho Sarri \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea), Napoli \u0111\u00e3 3  tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 11 b\u00e0n t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Liverpool.  Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia (Gozzano,  Carpi v\u00e0 Chievo). HLV Ancelotti v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1eefa  \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y Napoli sau 3 n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi  ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Liverpool vs Napoli giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 58 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Liverpool vs Napoli giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay 58 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Truc-tiep-Liverpool-vs-Napoli-giao-huu-CLB-he-2018-dem-nay-58-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Do \u0111\u00e3 s\u00e1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Liverpool n\u00ean &quot;L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf&quot; \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u1eadp  h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3  tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp trung. Ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Klopp m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng th\u1ee7  m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8  2018: Alisson Becker. \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Brazil c\u1ee7a Alisson, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Mane vs Salah t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng tr\u00ean  h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u01b0a th\u00edch 4-3-3 c\u1ee7a Klopp c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t  t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c: ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keita. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi &quot;L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf&quot; v\u00f9ng Merseyside  chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh \u01b0u th\u1ebf ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n 3 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3  ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Sadio Mane nh\u1ea3 ra ph\u00eda sau cho  James Milner ung dung \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i l\u00e0m ch\u00e1y g\u00f3c cao c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Napoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Serie A ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha uy hi\u1ebfp  \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Alisson nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y  tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 9 th\u00ec The Kop \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch  bi\u1ec7t. T\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, James Milner treo b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0  Wijnaldum b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e0ng d\u1eabn b\u00e0n s\u00e2u, Liverpool c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n. Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 s\u1eafc  b\u00e9n trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y m\u00f9a  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec Liverpool c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0 sau n\u1eeda hi\u1ec7p 1,  Napoli kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00f4t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 quanh \u0111i qu\u1ea9n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng  chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00f4 ph\u1ea1t \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n khi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u1eabn trong t\u1ea7m  ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng khan  hi\u1ebfm v\u00e0 2-0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9  thay m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Napoli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9  h\u00f2ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u00f2n Liverpool b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng  trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf t\u1eadp k\u00edch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 51, Sadio Mane d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i song c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m  cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mali ch\u1ec9 th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9  \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 58, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3. T\u00e2n binh Shaqiri t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i  v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1eaft c\u00f2i d\u00f9 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb Mane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Raul Albiol. Nh\u1edd  v\u1eady, Mohamed Salah m\u1edbi ung dung nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt  \u0111\u1ec3 g\u0103m tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o g\u00f3c cao trong s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 62, kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb9n m\u00e0 g\u1eb7p, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i  h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1edbi 5-6 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ph\u00fat 68, Daniel Sturridge  c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Napoli  \u1edf pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Sturridge x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba  Napoli tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa b\u1ea5m k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt qua \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karnezis nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i  b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 bay ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge Moreno\" title=\"Sturridge Moreno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Sturridge.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean Sturridge (tr\u00e1i) v\u00e0 Moreno (ph\u1ea3i) \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n cho Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 71 th\u00ec Sturridge kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00f4 duy\u00ean. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  g\u1eedi \u0111i tu nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Bundesliga, Origi d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Napoli r\u1ed3i  tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karnezis c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. B\u00f3ng b\u1eadt ra \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed  c\u1ee7a Sturridge v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi, ph\u00fat 76 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Sturridge ph\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00e1nh v\u00f4  c\u00f9ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c cho Moreno v\u00e0 sau v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp x\u1eed l\u00fd, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN tung ra c\u00fa n\u00e3  rocket h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Karnezis. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i sau khi  ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 5 c\u00f2n Liverpool v\u1eabn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Ph\u00fat 84,  Sturridge l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb9p cho Solanke nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh  kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Napoli trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, m\u1ed7i b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1-2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n song \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. 5-0 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u V\u0110QG \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 30 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nLIVERPOOL:</strong> Alisson, Clyne (Arnold 62'), Gomez, Van Dijk, Robertson (Moreno 62'), Wijnaldum (Jones 62'), Milner (Fabinho 55'), Keita (Origi 70'),  Salah (Sturridge 62'), Firmino (Shaqiri 46'), Mane (Solanke 62')<br>\r\n<strong>NAPOLI:</strong> Karnezis, Hysaj, Albiol (Maksimovic 61'), Koulibaly (Chiriches 72'), Luperto (Mario Rui 46', Diawara 62'), Allan, Hamsik (Rog 62'), Fabian,  Callejon (Inglese 62'), Milik (Verdi 62'), Insigne (Ounas 62')<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5086","checkdouble":"193724"},{"date":"01:00 05/08","title":"Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (KT): Los Blancos t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lopetegui ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t g\u1ecdn \"B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Juventus tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00fac 05h05 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8. Tuong thuat truc tiep, th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng pha b\u00f3ng video clip tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Juventus gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nDANH S\u00c1CH XU\u1ea4T PH\u00c1T<br>\r\nREAL MADRID (4-2-3-1):</strong> Keylor Navas; Dani Carvajal, Nacho, Javier S\u00e1nchez de Felipe, Sergio Reguilon; Toni Kroos, Federico Valverde; Gareth Bale, Isco, Dani Ceballos; Karim Benzema<br>\r\n<strong>JUVENTUS (4-1-4-1):</strong> Wojciech Szcz\u0119sny; Joao Cancelo, Medhi Benatia, Giorgio Chiellini, Mattia De Sciglio; Miralem Pjanic; Federico Bernardeschi, Sami Khedira, Claudio Marchisio, Alex Sandro; Andrea Favilli<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- HLV\u00a0Max Allegri \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Juventus m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Joao Cancelo c\u00f9ng Andrea Favilli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1. Trong \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi (Cancelo) m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y m\u00e0 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u0110N \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan c\u0169ng \u1edf Serie A theo di\u1ec7n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Valencia c\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi kia (Favalli) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho L\u00e3o b\u00e0 t\u1eeb Ascoli. Favalli t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 U20 FIFA World Cup 2017 (c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a U20 Vi\u1ec7t Nam) trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec3n Italia v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 hay \u1edf m\u1ea5y tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i b\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Real Madrid, \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV\u00a0xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb, Lopetegui trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb (4/11 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n) nh\u01b0ng 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\u00a0Navas, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nacho vs Carvajal, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung sau VCK\u00a0World Cup 2018 Toni Kroos hay tr\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Bale vs Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafp v\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Juventus nh\u1eadp  cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t Real Madrid ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn suy y\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3  so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung si\u00eau sao \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng to l\u1edbn do  Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 8: Bale \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ngay g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u  m\u00f4n Juventus, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do t\u01b0 th\u1ebf nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 12: JUVENTUS B\u1ea4T NG\u1edc GHI B\u00c0N.</strong> Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra  c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t tho\u00e1ng cho Cancelo v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng  ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o ph\u00eda trong. N\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a  b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-12.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 19: C\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n trong tay, Juventus c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh c\u1ee5c  di\u1ec7n trong khi Real d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n  g\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch khoan ph\u00e1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u  b\u1ea3ng Chiellini - Benatia. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb AC  Milan n\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 m\u00f9a  t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 25: Ng\u00f4i sao Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng  tr\u00fang khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-25.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 29: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Real hi\u1ec7n nay, Isco \u0111\u1ed9t nh\u1eadp  v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Juventus t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm song b\u00f3ng \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t  d\u1ecdc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-29.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 35: Nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh Juventus k\u00ecm gi\u1eef \u1edf m\u1ee9c ch\u1eadm h\u00f2ng l\u00e0m  gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 hung ph\u1ea5n v\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Real \u0111ang d\u1ea7n l\u00e2m v\u00e0o  b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong c\u00e1c b\u00e0i tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111e d\u1ecda n\u1ed5i khung  th\u00e0nh Szczesny.</p>\r\n<p><strong>- PH\u00daT 39: BALE G\u1ee0 H\u00d2A 1-1 CHO REAL.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic b\u1ecb gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng ngay b\u00ean  ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Gareth Bale v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3  lanh l\u1eb9 vung ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i s\u00fat uy l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng h\u01a1i s\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi  Benatia n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n n\u1ed5i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Szczesny.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-39.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 42: NGUY HI\u1ec2M. Sergio Reguilon, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 do ch\u00ednh Real  \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ra, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i r\u1ed3i vung ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i s\u00fat tr\u00e1i  ph\u00e1 nh\u1eb1m v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-42.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 45+1: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t thu\u1eadn ch\u00e2n d\u00e0nh cho Bale  nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n d\u00e0nh cho Szczesny khi b\u00f3ng \u0111i \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7  m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-46.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1. Juventus nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Carvajal. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thu m\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 khi b\u1ecb Bale s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<p><strong>HI\u1ec6P 2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao. Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ebfn 5 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Bale, Isco,  Kroos, Benzema, Carvajal r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Marcos Llorente, Vin\u00edcius  J\u00fanior, Marco Asensio, Lucas Vazquez c\u00f9ng <span class=\"text\">Odriozola. Trong \u0111\u00f3  Odriozola v\u00e0 Vin\u00edcius l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><strong><span class=\"text\">- PH\u00daT 47: REAL V\u01af\u01a0N L\u00caN D\u1eaaN 2-1. </span></strong><span class=\"text\">Ch\u00ednh hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a  Real \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng nhanh, Vin\u00edcius J\u00fanior - ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil sinh n\u0103m 2000 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m  ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Real h\u01a1n 46 tri\u1ec7u Euro ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng - t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng  c\u1ea5m r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng c\u0103ng ngang cho Asensio lao v\u00e0o s\u00fat c\u0103ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Juventus. </span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-47.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 53: Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t kh\u00e1 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i khi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed g\u1ea7n v\u1ea1ch 16m50  v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1i l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Lucas Vazquez th\u1eadm ch\u00ed  c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng qua n\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o ch\u1eafn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>- PH\u00daT 56: 3-1 CHO REAL MADRID.</strong> K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111ang n\u1ed5 ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Fedex  Field. M\u1ed9t Real tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t  tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 gia tang c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean 2 b\u00e0n. Nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb Vazquez, Marco Asensio \u0111\u1ea9y  b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e9o \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 theo k\u00e8m r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i. B\u00f3ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng  c\u0103ng song v\u1eabn h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Szczesny c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-56.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 60:\u00a0B\u1ece L\u1ee0! Vinicius, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh \"Neymar m\u1edbi\", c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Juventus \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 66: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. V\u1eeba m\u1edbi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho \u0111\u00e0n anh Keylor Navas, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb  Lunin \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n c\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joao Cancelo.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-65.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 68: NGUY HI\u1ec2M. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pjanic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t  ng\u1edd khi chuy\u1ec1n nh\u1eb9 cho trung v\u1ec7 Chiellini. G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng  kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lunin lao  ra truy c\u1ea3n k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-68.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 75: Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 qua, Juventus \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Allegri v\u1eabn \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 78: Matheus Pereira - ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil - quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh  th\u1eed v\u1eadn may \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly xa v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus-78.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p>- PH\u00daT 81: Lunin, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ukraine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid chi\u00eau m\u1ed9  m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 pha c\u1ee9u thua t\u1ed1t sau m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 85: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. Pha treo b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Trung v\u1ec7 Rugani n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Real.</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5085","checkdouble":"193731"},{"date":"03:00 05/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP AC Milan vs Barca 07h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/ac-milan-vs-barca-tran-dau-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp AC Milan vs Barca: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 AC Milan vs Barcelona tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 07h05 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN XUNG QUANH<br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Barca thua 6, th\u1eafng 4/10 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Milan.<br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Milan th\u1eafng 6, thua 2/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n- Theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Barca thua 5, h\u00f2a 1, th\u1eafng 2/8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n6/8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1. 3/4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Milan c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p 1. 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Barca x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Do v\u1eady, hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nBarcelona: Cillessen, Cucurella, Lenglet, Marlon, Semedo, Roberto, Collado, Arthur, Malcom, Munir, Aleix Vidal<br>\r\nMilan: Donnarumma, Calabria, Romagnoli, Musacchio, Abate, Locatelli, Kessie, Bonaventura, Calhanoglu, Suso, Andre Silva\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/1/barca-2-4-roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5084","checkdouble":"193733"},{"date":"06:04 05/08","title":"Arsenal 2-0 Lazio: H\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/arsenal-20-lazio-hung-phan-buoc-vao-mua-giai-moi-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 \u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: ARSENAL 2-0 LAZIO\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Arsenal-vs-Lazio.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi d\u00e0n h\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. C\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd Lazio c\u0169ng c\u00f3 cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Sergej Milinkovi\u0107-Savi\u0107 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFelipe Caicedo tung c\u00fa v\u00f4 l\u00ea nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ebf, b\u1ed9 ba ng\u00f4i sao Reiss Nelson, Alex Iwobi v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alexandre Lacazette tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat th\u1ee9 17 Nelson \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sau c\u00fa s\u00fat nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Iwobi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Silvio Proto. Arsenal v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lazio v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Arsenal vs Lazio 2-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Arsenal vs Lazio 2-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/0_pre-season-friendly-lazio-v-arsenal-1-0528.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a HLV Emery ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00ed b\u00f3ng k\u0129 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u00f4i qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Simone Inzaghi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Lazio l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u1ef3 \u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat th\u1ee9 63 kh\u1edfi ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb Elneny, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lacazette tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p nh\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang tung c\u00fa s\u00fat hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Lazio. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 2-0 cho Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u1ea3nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Leno. I Biancocelesti \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c: Arsenal 2-0 Lazio<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n: Nelson (17'), Aubameyang (63').<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n<br>\r\nArsenal: Leno, Lichsteiner, Chambers, Holding, Maitland-Niles, Nelson, Xhaka, Torreira, Iwobi, Lacazette, Nketiah.<br>\r\nLazio: Proto, Wallace, Acerbi, Radu Basta, Parolo, Leiva, Murgia, Lulic, Luis Alberto, Caicedo.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5083","checkdouble":"193742"},{"date":"06:28 05/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/31/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-58-lo-muc-gia-de-mu-so-huu-alderweireld.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 5/8.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nL\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mirror, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Tottenham, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f2i 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng M.U bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Alderweireld ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8 L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 58 L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 MU s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/Truoc-nhung-tin-don-Toby-Alderweireld-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Perisic l\u1ea1i th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb &ldquo;m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;, v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ivan Perisic cho bi\u1ebft v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Inter, v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Milan t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu 2 ng\u00f4i sao l\u00e0 Higuain v\u00e0 Calfara t\u1eeb Juventus, Rossoneri ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i h\u1ecfi mua sao tr\u1ebb Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Lazio v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mua \u0111\u1ee9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o m\u00f9a sau. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Savic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Modric<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia c\u0169ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modric l\u00e0 750 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8\" title=\"Modric v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-257-MU-tong-tan-cong-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: Modric \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Emirates &ndash; Lucas Perez \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua t\u1eeb Sporting Lisbon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t: 4,45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, khi nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5082","checkdouble":"193743"},{"date":"19:33 04/08","title":"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/cuc-nong-pogba-da-chon-xong-so-ao-o-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CalcioMarceto ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Andres Iniesta. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Rafinha v\u00e0 Andre Gomes \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o, Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Chon-xong-so-ao,-Paul-Pogba-toi-Barca-chi-la-van-de-thoi-gian-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba-180-192489.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca quan t\u00e2m Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a La Liga hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Old Trafford, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u00eda Barca \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Eric Abidal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ri\u00eang Pogba, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Camp Nou. Abidal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Pogba m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Paul Pogba t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CalcioMarceto ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba vo dich the gioi\" title=\"Pogba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-38-barca-quyet-no-bom-tan-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba ch\u1ecdn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 \u1edf Barca hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eb7c trong h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m qua. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPogba y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Barca gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 l\u1ea1i cho m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u sao Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng M.U nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio ho\u1eb7c Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5081","checkdouble":"193721"},{"date":"20:58 04/08","title":"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/25/cac-ngoi-sao-cua-real-madrid-khong-hai-long-voi-sergio-ramos.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eadp trung qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 Real \u01b0u \u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm, c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Cac-ngoi-sao-cua-Real-Madrid-khong-hai-long-voi-Sergio-Ramos-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real \u01b0u \u00e1i sau World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u1eafn sau World Cup 2018, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIsco, Marco Asensio, Lucas Vasquez v\u00e0 Nacho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 25 v\u00e0 26 th\u00e1ng 7, t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y 29/7 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dani Carvajal t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 01/08 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Sergio Ramos v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Ramos</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra ghen t\u1ef5 khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 l\u00e2u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/cac-ngoi-sao-cua-real-madrid-khong-hai-long-voi-sergio-ramos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Sergio Ramos</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Marca, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Real \u0111\u00e3 than v\u00e3n v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ramos t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 c\u0169ng h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Marca, Ramos \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamos gia nh\u1eadp Real n\u0103m 2005 t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Los Blancos c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 La Liga v\u00e0 4 Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5080","checkdouble":"193726"},{"date":"21:38 04/08","title":"HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/10/12/MU-ap-dao-doi-hinh-te-nhat-vong-9-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Barca khen ng\u1ee3i Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p khi\u1ebfn M.U ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh, anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" title=\"tien ve Pogba M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/20/andy-cole-khong-danh-gia-cao-paul-pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Barca khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Pogba th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nErnesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Pogba trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, song Pogba th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M.U ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Valverde n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Barca \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Paul Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Ernesto-Valverde-phat-bieu-ve-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Sport c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/cuc-nong-pogba-da-chon-xong-so-ao-o-barca-180-193721.html\" target=\"_blank\">Pogba ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca</span>, anh s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 do huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, HLV Valverde n\u00f3i th\u00eam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u1edf c\u1eeda, Barca v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Barca c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m Pogba hay kh\u00f4ng \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n mua b\u00e1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarcelona m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern Munich v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Paulinho \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5079","checkdouble":"193728"},{"date":"22:30 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-co-matteo-darmian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Matteo Darmian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Jose Mourinho, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn anh ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu-172-193679.html\" target=\"_blank\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian</span>, Juventus, Roma v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn Mourinho mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Darmian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Benfica mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Benfica mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Benfica-muon-co-Matteo-Darmian-cua-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benfica mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Darmian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Darmian \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u00e0 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19\u00a0tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Benfica \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn M.U h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford mu\u1ed1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Benfica, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Darmian. Hi\u1ec7n Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u1ef1u sao Torino c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5078","checkdouble":"193732"}]}